briefdescription.para: Error code for MS5611 specific functions.
Minimum raw temperature measurement for error checking.

simplesect.title: Description:
simplesect.para: The minimum value of temperature for the MS5611 for temperature validation. Equal to -40 degrees Celsius.

simplesect.title: Limits:
simplesect.para: Must be defined as a minimum numeric value of the raw MS5611 temperature measurement.

briefdescription.para: Maximum raw temperature measurement for error checking.

simplesect.title: Description:
simplesect.para: The maximum value of temperature for the MS5611 for temperature validation. Equal to 85 degrees Celsius.

simplesect.title: Limits:
simplesect.para: Must be defined as a maximum numeric value of the raw MS5611 temperature measurement.

briefdescription.para: Minimum raw pressure measurement for error checking.

simplesect.title: Description:
simplesect.para: The minimum value of pressure for the MS5611 for pressure validation.

simplesect.title: Limits:
simplesect.para: Must be defined as a minimum numeric value of the raw MS5611 pressure measurement.

briefdescription.para: Maximum raw pressure measurement for error checking.

simplesect.title: Description:
simplesect.para: The maximum value of pressure for the MS5611 for pressure validation.

simplesect.title: Limits:
simplesect.para: Must be defined as a maximum numeric value of the raw MS5611 pressure measurement.
